Where is Woodburn Located?

Woodburn is a city located in the Marion County of Oregon, United States. Woodburn lies between 35.612661 Degrees North latitudes and 77.3663538 Degrees West longitudes. According to 2020 U.S.census, the population of Woodburn city is 26013 people and the city has a total area of 5.84 sq mi. The city has numerous parks and recreational facilities.
